#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.power.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.power"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:1 of
msgid ""
"Draws samples in [0, 1] from a power distribution with positive exponent "
"a - 1."
msgstr "从正指数为 a - 1 的幂律分布中抽取 [0, 1] 区间内的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:4 of
msgid "Also known as the power function distribution."
msgstr "也称为幂函数分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:6 of
msgid "Parameter of the distribution. Should be greater than zero."
msgstr "分布的参数。应大于零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:8 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``a`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(a).size`` samples "
"are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），当 ``a`` 为标量时返回单个值。否则抽取 ``mt"
".array(a).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:13 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:15 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:17 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:20 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized power distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的幂律分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:23 of
msgid "If a < 1."
msgstr "如果 a < 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:27 of
msgid "The probability density function is"
msgstr "概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:29 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"P(x; a) = ax^{a-1}, 0 \\le x \\le 1, a>0.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:31 of
msgid ""
"The power function distribution is just the inverse of the Pareto "
"distribution. It may also be seen as a special case of the Beta "
"distribution."
msgstr "幂函数分布是帕累托分布的逆分布。它也可以看作是 Beta 分布的特例。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:35 of
msgid ""
"It is used, for example, in modeling the over-reporting of insurance "
"claims."
msgstr "例如，它可用于建模保险索赔的过度报告。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:39 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:40 of
msgid ""
"Christian Kleiber, Samuel Kotz, \"Statistical size distributions in "
"economics and actuarial sciences\", Wiley, 2003."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:42 of
msgid ""
"Heckert, N. A. and Filliben, James J. \"NIST Handbook 148: Dataplot "
"Reference Manual, Volume 2: Let Subcommands and Library Functions\", "
"National Institute of Standards and Technology Handbook Series, June "
"2003. "
"http://www.itl.nist.gov/div898/software/dataplot/refman2/auxillar/powpdf.pdf"
msgstr ""
"Heckert, N. A. 和 Filliben, James J. \"NIST Handbook 148: Dataplot "
"Reference Manual, Volume 2: Let Subcommands and Library Functions\", "
"国家标准与技术研究院手册系列, 2003年6月. http://www.itl.nist.gov/div898/"
"software/dataplot/refman2/auxillar/powpdf.pdf"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:49 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:50 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:58 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.power.power:69 of
msgid "Compare the power function distribution to the inverse of the Pareto."
msgstr "将幂函数分布与帕累托分布的逆进行比较。"

